data.description: This home is conveniently located in the sought after Whisper Lakes Community!  The roof was changed in February 2023 and the AC in 2022.  The spacious living room and dining room are an open floor concept, with tile flooring, ceiling fan and new lighting fixtures, with sliding door that access  a semi private fenced porch.  Kitchen with beautiful wood cabinets, granite counters, stainless steel appliances and eating space.  Bedrooms with laminated flooring, master bedroom with sliding doors giving access to a fenced yard.  Master bathroom with wood cabinet and dual sink.  The community is near restaurants, shopping malls, main roads, highways and toll roads.   The Villages has a community pool with tennis court, playground area and pool
